# ⑦ live model sweep — evidence (2026-07-17)

Runner: scripts/live_model_sweep.py → shipped src/agents/ai/model_sweep.py
(live_router_factory + run_sweep + resume dedup), local MLX endpoint
http://127.0.0.1:18090/v1 (mlx_lm.server, per-request dynamic model load).
Dataset: ROUTING_EVAL_SET (20 cases incl. 5 adversarial). Spend: $0 (local
inference). effort axis → sampling temperature (low=0.0, high=1.0).
Total live calls: 160 (4 configs × 20 cases × 2 prompt versions), unparsed
replies → backstop: 0 in every run (deterministic backstop never fired).

